<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard - Bot Oficial</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #05070a;
            --accent-blue: #3b82f6;
            --accent-purple: #8b5cf6;
            --glass-bg: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
            --border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }
        
        body { 
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; 
            background-color: var(--bg-dark); 
            color: #f8fafc;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .bg-mesh {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 0% 0%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 40%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 40%);
        }

        .glass { 
            background: var(--glass-bg); 
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px); 
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color); 
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .sidebar-item {
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .sidebar-item::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0; top: 0; height: 100%; width: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-blue), transparent);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .active-nav { 
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15), transparent);
            color: #60a5fa;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-blue);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .stat-card {
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
        }

        .stat-icon-bg {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1), rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1));
        }

        .glow-text {
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
        }

        @keyframes pulse-slow {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
        }
        .pulse-soft { animation: pulse-slow 3s infinite ease-in-out; }
    </style>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            const path = window.location.pathname;
            if (path === '/') document.getElementById('nav-home').classList.add('active-nav');
            if (path === '/embeds') document.getElementById('nav-embeds').classList.add('active-nav');
            if (path === '/staff') document.getElementById('nav-staff').classList.add('active-nav');
        });
    </script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex">
    <div class="bg-mesh"></div>

    <!-- Sidebar -->
    <aside class="w-72 glass border-r border-slate-800 p-8 flex flex-col z-10">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-12">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">V</span>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">
                OFICIAL<span class="text-blue-500">BOT</span>
            </h1>
        </div>

        <nav class="space-y-3 flex-1">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 ml-2">Menu Principal</p>
            <a href="/" id="nav-home" class="sidebar-item flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 rounded-xl text-slate-400 hover:text-white group transition-all">
                <span class="text-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">🏠</span>
                <span class="font-medium">Overview</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/embeds" id="nav-embeds" class="sidebar-item flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 rounded-xl text-slate-400 hover:text-white group transition-all">
                <span class="text-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">📑</span>
                <span class="font-medium">Embed Studio</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/staff" id="nav-staff" class="sidebar-item flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 rounded-xl text-slate-400 hover:text-white group transition-all">
                <span class="text-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">👑</span>
                <span class="font-medium">Equipo Staff</span>
            </a>
            
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 pt-8 ml-2">Moderación</p>
            <a href="#" class="sidebar-item flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 rounded-xl text-slate-400 opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed">
                <span>🛡️</span>
                <span class="font-medium">Logs System</span>
            </a>
            <a href="#" class="sidebar-item flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 rounded-xl text-slate-400 opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed">
                <span>⚠️</span>
                <span class="font-medium">Warnings</span>
            </a>
        </nav>

        <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-800/50">
            <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-4 flex items-center space-x-4 border-slate-700/30">
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-full bg-slate-800 border-2 border-blue-500/30 overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/embed/avatars/0.png" alt="Bot Avatar" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 rounded-full border-2 border-[#0f172a]"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="overflow-hidden">
                    <p class="text-sm font-bold truncate"><%= botName %></p>
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-blue-400 font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">Online Now</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </aside>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-1 p-12 overflow-y-auto">
        <header class="flex justify-between items-center mb-16">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-3 tracking-tight">Panel de <span class="text-blue-500">Control</span></h2>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">Monitorea el rendimiento de tu bot oficial en tiempo real.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex space-x-4">
                <div class="glass px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-400">📅</span>
                    <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300"><%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('es-ES') %></span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Stats Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
            <div class="stat-card glass p-8 rounded-[2rem] border-b-4 border-blue-600/50">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl stat-icon-bg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">🌍</div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-400 bg-blue-400/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest">Servidores</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-5xl font-black mb-1 glow-text tracking-tighter"><%= guildCount %></p>
                <p class="text-slate-500 font-semibold text-sm">Guilds Conectadas</p>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-card glass p-8 rounded-[2rem] border-b-4 border-purple-600/50">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">👥</div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-400 bg-purple-400/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest">Alcance</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-5xl font-black mb-1 tracking-tighter"><%= userCount %></p>
                <p class="text-slate-500 font-semibold text-sm">Usuarios Totales</p>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-card glass p-8 rounded-[2rem] border-b-4 border-green-600/50">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">⚡</div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-green-400 bg-green-400/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest">Latencia</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-baseline space-x-2">
                    <p class="text-5xl font-black mb-1 tracking-tighter"><%= ping %></p>
                    <span class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-500">ms</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-500 font-semibold text-sm">WebSocket Delay</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <!-- System Health -->
            <div class="glass p-10 rounded-[2.5rem]">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-8">
                    <div class="w-2 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Estado del Núcleo</h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 glass rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/30 border-slate-700/50">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                            <span class="text-2xl">⏱️</span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Tiempo Activo</p>
                                <p class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-400 font-mono"><%= uptime %></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 glass rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/30 border-slate-700/50">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                            <span class="text-2xl">💾</span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Base de Datos</p>
                                <p class="text-xl font-bold text-green-400">Cloud Postgres</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-green-500/10 text-green-500 text-[10px] font-black rounded-full border border-green-500/20 uppercase tracking-widest">Active</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 glass rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/30 border-slate-700/50">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                            <span class="text-2xl">🚀</span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Versión Engine</p>
                                <p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-300">Node v20.x</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Quick Action -->
            <div class="glass p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600/10 to-purple-600/10 relative overflow-hidden group">
                <div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-blue-600/20 transition-all duration-700"></div>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-4 relative z-10">¿Necesitas enviar un anuncio?</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mb-10 relative z-10 max-w-xs">Accede al estudio de diseño de embeds para crear mensajes impactantes.</p>
                
                <a href="/embeds" class="inline-flex items-center space-x-3 bg-white text-black font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-blue-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-xl relative z-10">
                    <span>Ir a Embed Studio</span>
                    <span class="text-xl">➡️</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>